{"tid":435164,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"作為前Pixel 用家，表示iPhone 6S 都好用過佢","createTime":"2017-10-14T04:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T01:33:00.000Z","uid":63866,"like":35,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"589ab74e08c29ea17d92c94cb19e8641b7cc5ec2","tid":435164,"uid":63866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"本身用iPhone 5, 出左Pixel 既時候就想轉返用Android , 因為之前覺得moto milestone 好正<br />\n<br />\n用左大半年，打傳說對決又load 得慢過人，wifi 又唔stable, 電又用得快，話就話有快差，但係部機又熱又唔係快好多，根本就係粒U 垃圾哂電，仲要有時有啲位都係lag lag 地<br />\n<br />\n出左iPhone 8 &amp; X, 即刻狗衝換返6s<br />\n<br />\n而加見到啲人吹棒 pixel 2 真心覺得on lun 9<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 有無人要二手Pixel 32GB 黑色 (爆左後玻璃）"},{"pid":"42ae44f4adc85e479da3297fa7812acc165a4c22","tid":435164,"uid":81397,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"踩到一文不值咁賣機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f686a7b3022a95fd4c8be2c50c1038ae2530dd9","tid":435164,"uid":4524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"HKD$500收你部 pixel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00889582dc9786fee00b1c4ccaefe9bb21e69638","tid":435164,"uid":63866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:37:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩到一文不值咁賣機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身諗住當後備機，但係見隔離post 係咁吹棒，有人出價我咪賣<br />\n反正後備機都唔係咁想用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf62c43dca33978cda26803b55e60ac314d4d283","tid":435164,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"換6s, 下